---
// src/components/Hero/Hero.astro
---

<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="container hero-container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>
        <span class="light">Proteja seu futuro</span><br />
        <span class="light">com os nossos</span><br />
        <span class="bold">Seguros e Consórcios Personalizados</span>
      </h1>
      <p>
        Oferecemos proteção e planejamento para o que é mais<br />
        importante na sua vida, garantindo segurança e tranquilidade<br />
        para você e sua família alcançarem seus maiores objetivos.
      </p>
      <button
        class="btn-primary mt-6"
        id="open-budget-dialog-hero"
        style="margin-top: 32px;"
      >
        SIMULAR CONSÓRCIO
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-image-placeholder">
      <img src="/house.png" alt="Casa" class="hero-img" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 850px;
    background-color: white;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-section::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 63%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, white 10%, transparent 50%);
    z-index: 3;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    padding-bottom: 180px;
    max-width: 1560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-content {
    color: #111111;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: #111111;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .hero-content h1 .light {
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero-content h1 .bold {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #444444;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .hero-image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .hero-img {
    width: 130%;
    max-width: 1600px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-right: -340px;
    margin-bottom: -180px;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .hero-section::after {
      display: none;
    }

    .hero-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .hero-content h1,
    .hero-content p {
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    #open-budget-dialog-hero {
      margin-left: 0 !important;
    }

    .hero-image-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-img {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
